snippet.title: Jimmy Snow
snippet.description:
Hi all! I am Jimmy Snow! 

I grew up as a deeply religious person and have seen first hand how dangerous religions can be in controlling minds and behavior. My channel exists to try and balance that and help others to see there is a happy, healthy world waiting for them on the other side of religion! 

***Support the Channel***

Patreon - http://bit.ly/2PkRJt0 (Be my hero!)

One Time Donation (Paypal) - http://bit.ly/2RID6wY
Amazon Wishlist: http://bit.ly/2Ps5RMd
Shirts and Merch- http://bit.ly/2TWO7w2 (Save 10% code: Bethany)
Audible- Trial- https://amzn.to/2NHjV7K (2 Free Books)

----------------------------------------------------
Subreddit: http://bit.ly/mrathsubreddit
Other Channel (Live Shows): http://bit.ly/2Ep5PCV
Email List: http://bit.ly/2BUiPyQ (Never miss a show)
Discord - http://bit.ly/2DyLFqx (Best Place to Hang)
Twitch - http://bit.ly/2Deauam 
Twitter - http://bit.ly/2S9jCBf (Where I get weird)
Instagram - http://bit.ly/2PkXAtu
Contact - dearmratheist@gmail.com
